message: "Talking about it, bringing awareness is probably the best way to start. That's why I'm getting my blue streak!" said Jenna Taylor, a client at the salon Thursday who wanted to wanted to help make a difference.  "How many people it is affecting, I just, I don't know, on a whim I said I want to do it, I want to do something to help!"

attachments.media_description: Salons dying 'blue streaks' in hair for human trafficking awareness month
